Distribution. This species was previously reported from the Japanese coast (
Imajima 1990
), the Atlantic coast of Spain (
Moreira et al. 2000
), the Aegean Sea (
Pancucci–Papadopoulou et al. 2005
; Dagli et al. in press) and the Sea of Marmara (
Çinar et al. 2011 a
). This species is being newly reported from Levantine and the Black Sea coasts of Turkey .
